                                text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;>Can a new approach help accelerate the pace of scientific research and be kinder to the environment?&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
